aped Headquarters Building for the Pacific Fleet and a tank farm at right. Note one tank painted as a building.'></a></td></tr></table><a href='/photo.php?source=all&color=all&list=search&foreigntype=S&foreigntype_id=303'>See all 14 photographs of Heavy Cruiser USS Pensacola</a><br /><br /><br /><br />
